                <a class="featured-thumbnail" href="https://www.ct.org.tw/1342052" title="靈修生活提不起勁嗎？">
                 <img alt="4117_靈修生活提不起勁嗎？" class="attachment-featured wp-post-image" height="215" src="https://www.ct.org.tw/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/4117_靈修生活提不起勁嗎？-373x215.gif" width="373"/>
